my heroine who had remained in Russia. This appeared in Rul’ (Berlin, January 29, 1925) as “Pis’mo (Letter) v Rossiyu,” and was collected in Vozvrashchenie Chorba, in Berlin, 1930. A literal rendering of the title would have been ambiguous and therefore had to be changed.

